<h1>Executive Summary</h1>
<p id ="exec-summary-text">The following is a report written to fullfill the requirements of the Property On Line (POL) Project for the classes SUTN 2018: Technical Writing and SUTN 2013: Legal Aspects of Surveying, at the Centre of Geographic Sciences (COGS) in Lawrencetown, Nova Scotia. This report details the findings of the author; Liam Osler, on the subject of a property located in the area of North Preston, Nova Scotia. The main subject property is identified by the PID number 00495390 and the properties are located around the 1100 block of Downey Road. To process used to complete this project is detailed in the methods and scope of work sections of this report.